     I felt a need to come here and offer my and my guilds support once again to Creapiing due to an event with Akmorph tonight.  <br>
     On my first ever trip to the rant board I came across the whole situation.  It was my first sight at such a disrespectful sight.  I personally do not know creapiing but due to the enormous amounts of posts in support I knew that you were a very nice and kind person.  Since we are a new guild, and a majority of our players our new to eq I thought this would be a good example for my guild.  So I posted the situation on our board so we could discuss the event.<br>
     Well tonight a group of 5 from TFB were killing at the orc fort in EW.  3 died and Akmorph walks by about 2 minutes after.  He offers to rez the dead.  All members in the party had read what happened and they commenced to decline his rez offers.  Stating a stance in beliefs and morals with such a disrespectful person.  Akmorph gets offended and asks to talk to one of our leaders.  Being PR officer he is sent to me.  He tells me that he offered rezzes but they were refused and that he was very offended.  I told him that we appreciated his offer but that due to many hard feelings over this situation we could not accept.  He told me that most had forgiven him and that we needed to move on.  I told him that may be, but that we had not.  Our conversation ended there.<br>
     The guild asked me to come here and post this so you know that you are respected for who you are and how you uphold yourself Creapiing.  To let you know that such events will not be tolerated or condoned among us.  We were very proud to stand beside you and lend our support in this event.<br>
